c: 10
v: 49
t: "Vuga (yewe Muhamadi) uti \"Ku bwanjye, nta bushobozi mfite bwo kugira ikibi nakwikiza cyangwa ngo ngire icyiza nakwimarira uretse icyo Allahyashaka. Buri muryango (umat) wagenewe igihe ntarengwa (cyo kubaho); iyo igihe cyabo kigeze, ntibarindirizwa na gato cyangwa ngo bihutishwe mbere yacyo"